  "monster": {
    "title": "Ezxalag.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Ezxalag has a muscular body with hideous, tattered wings and a skull for a head. It changes colour whenever you look at it.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 199     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++ +   </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: +         </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: +..     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: ++.      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 150% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 85% to hit with the +3 Elemental Staff.\nIt has about 80% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  \nHit     49          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeted by your fire vortex.",
